title: A Roman Walks into a Bar...
body: Holds up 2 fingers and says “Five Beers Please!”

replies.body: Hmm... do Romans bros (officially known as Bromans) do "high eights" instead of "high fives"?
As long as they use their right hand.
I think it works better on the left hand actually. The thumb and pointer form the V and the remaining three fingers are the III.
sorry i'm more into greek history.

I wonder how many people won't get the joke.
